Installation 
1. Download prometheus package from prometheus.io site
  Prometheus-2.17.1.linu-amd64.targ.gz

2. Extract the package 
   # tar -xvf Prometheus-2.17.1.linu-amd64.targ.gz

3. Enter into the direcotory 
   # cd Prometheus-2.17.1.linu-amd64

4. start the prometheus service 
   #./prometheus

5. Access the prometheus page
   # http://192.168.0.101:9090/graph

             
